[
  {
    "text": "Greetings. Bill Nye here.",
    "start": 0.882,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to the Disaster Institute.",
    "start": 2.992,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "Earth is constantly on the edge of disaster.",
    "start": 5.489,
    "duration": 2.878
  },
  {
    "text": "Viewer discretion is advised.",
    "start": 12.291,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "Why is it that every disaster movie",
    "start": 15.379,
    "duration": 2.419
  },
  {
    "text": "begins with someone in power\nignoring a scientist?",
    "start": 17.798,
    "duration": 3.587
  },
  {
    "text": "People are sick of all the doom and gloom.",
    "start": 21.643,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "Because it happens\nmore than you might think.",
    "start": 24.021,
    "duration": 1.919
  },
  {
    "text": "This is gonna really suck.",
    "start": 26.87,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Nuts?",
    "start": 29.112,
    "duration": 0.751
  },
  {
    "text": "It doesn't have to go down that way.",
    "start": 31.621,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Together we can save Earth,",
    "start": 33.671,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "with science.",
    "start": 36.139,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "Join me as I take on six world-ending disasters.",
    "start": 37.467,
    "duration": 3.587
  },
  {
    "text": "Each one",
    "start": 44.048,
    "duration": 1.252
  },
  {
    "text": "leading to my imminent doom.",
    "start": 45.94,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "Brace yourselves!",
    "start": 48.067,
    "duration": 1.209
  },
  {
    "text": "So yeah, I guess you could say",
    "start": 50.877,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "I really am dying to save the world.",
    "start": 52.67,
    "duration": 2.086
  }
]